3. [Scanner skipping input, possible white space?](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/39118045/scanner-skipping-input-possible-white-space)

An better but slower solution involves using  [BufferedReader](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/16/docs/api/java.base/java/io/BufferedReader.html) for reading any input from any input stream see [Scanner vs. BufferedReader](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2231369/scanner-vs-bufferedreader)

